headline: Is It Too Late To Consider TE Connectivity After Its 2024 Share Price Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether TE Connectivity is still worth considering after such a strong run, or if the easy gains are already behind it, this piece will walk through what the current share price really implies about potential future returns. The stock has pulled back slightly over the last week, down about 0.1%, but it is still up roughly 5.0% over 30 days, 63.5% year to date, and an impressive 62.6% over the past year.
